## GOAL / PURPOSE

2D slice-based diffusion model for brain MRI synthesis using a skull-stripped,
multi-modal brain MRI dataset (T1, T2-axi, T2-cor, FLAIR).
**Current decision: train on 3D volumetric subjects only, T1 modality first.**

