## KNOWN CONSTRAINTS / GOTCHAS

1. **Two populations** must not be mixed — thick-slice (4–7mm) and 3D (0.4–2mm) are incompatible slice thicknesses.
2. **3D volumes need cropping** — ~43% of slices are empty padding.
3. **Heterogeneous shapes** — 52 unique spatial configs, must resample to canonical 256×256 @ 1mm.
4. **Missing modalities** — not all subjects have all modalities; loaders must handle absent files.
5. **Empty volume** — X4DSUZALBB has 0 usable T1 slices, must be dropped.
6. **MONAI not installed yet.**
7. **No train/val/test split defined yet** — Step 4 above is the plan.
8. **No model code exists yet.**

